  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the purpose of the study is to extend the use of Rasagelin Mesylate 1mg per day by subjects
      who participated in the Adagio TVP 1012/501 according to form 4a for additional three years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
