        subjects who took part in the TVP 1012/501 clinical trial and willing to contiue receiving
        Rasgiline Mesylate.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  subjects who are willing to contiue this treatment.

